{"tid":1438111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[We Connect] Connect 埋新移民得唔得? 文宣篇","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:00:01.000Z","uid":218313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6dd655ef78d02b633e46ac20d121073a97f93a","tid":1438111,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">出得呢個post 就預左俾人屌</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新移民係好多連登仔心中既一條刺, 但係<span style=\"color: blue;\">新移民中其實都有支持運動既人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但由於<span style=\"color: blue;\">長期係受終國式文化影響</span>, 可能唔敢表達出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者係仲未諗通運動失敗對自己有乜影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地落左黎已成定局, 與其俾<span style=\"color: navy;\">建制狗</span>拉晒佢地做票倉, 不如試下Connect 一下佢地</span></span></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟覺得對新移民文宣要以<span style=\"color: green;\">簡單</span>/<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔HARD SELL</span>/<span style=\"color: violet;\">中立為主</span><br />\n一句起兩句止, 用簡體字, 等佢地反思一下<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>人生意義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>例子一:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得香港好嗎?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">那如果香港明天變得深圳一樣呢?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>例子二:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得香港食物安全嗎?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">那如果明天香港食物再不安全呢?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>例子三:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得香港自由嗎?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">那如果明天香港再沒有自由呢?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>例子四:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得香港可以維權嗎?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">那如果明天起香港再不能維權呢?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係新移民中都好多<span style=\"color: red;\">死藍屍同死腦筋</span>, 做文宣貼完就要走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點係新移民屋村, 巴士站等<br />\n<br />\n大家討論一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8f7dd83fd2c23b9f8cc473615f099f7f11f5b8","tid":1438111,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/csY2Lmh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcsY2Lmh.jpg&h=594ca6f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRgzBsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRgzBsX.jpg&h=b85f17b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bhfc7zT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbhfc7zT.jpg&h=5c6ae288&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bc8ebac0b18197c29bdb0fd0ad61e640109d79d","tid":1438111,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"新移民死全家"},{"pid":"e8f694f132f8f6de8adea2863f03b486a4409dc6","tid":1438111,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc8ebac0b18197c29bdb0fd0ad61e640109d79d","tid":1438111,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"新移民死全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n革命係要令唔支持你既人, 變得支持你"},{"pid":"93e8c6fcf896431d79543f8b4ddc3d15c5e6c0e8","tid":1438111,"uid":142735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:47:43.000Z","msg":"We connect<br />\n順便輸出民主"},{"pid":"8d9a684f1383a955f12be89495a4ff6cb38016d9","tid":1438111,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93e